reviews.name: VeggieTales: Josh & The Big Wall (Full Frame)
reviews.reviewText: This is a wonderful movie for kids and adults too! My son loves Veggie Tails as do I for their great message and fun songs. This particular one is about being obedient to God. They are all great Bible stories changed a little for the kids but all include some very funny stuff that only the parents would get. Love my Veggie Tails!
reviews.title: very cute movie!

reviews.name: VeggieTales: Josh & The Big Wall (Full Frame)
reviews.reviewText: My two year old loves it. She refers to it as the "Ewww" veggie tales video, since a few of the scenes are of the little peas dumping slushies on the other veggies marching around the wall. She always says "Ewww" during this scene - too cute! ( :
reviews.title: Wonderful video!

reviews.name: VeggieTales: Josh & The Big Wall (Full Frame)
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this for my 9-year old and wasn't sure if he would still find it interesting, but he has watched it twice and enjoyed it each time. I especially like the message it sends to kids about being obedient.
reviews.title: 16 August 2013
